Map was made in 5 mintues...

There are many weapons on the ground, ump's and mac10's at the spawns.  There is an outer-circle, where player's spawn, a mid-way circle which is nothing special, and a inner-circle where there are teleport's which take the player's to the top floor.  On the base floor cover is provided by block-like things in the ground.  On the top, there are tall structures which a player can run into, their are long glass bridges leading to those structures.  This map is pretty big (about 4048x4048).  This is the third map i've made.  PM me for request's.

You may not re-release this map elsewhere!

This map contains a couple of changes to one of my other maps, dm_scoutingouting, that provide a completely different gaming experience.

1. A spawn house was added for each team, with a team-specific buy zone, giving the newly-spawned protection and choice as to what gun to use.

2. The middle stone wall was moved so as to give the spawned protection while coming out of their spawn house.

3. A bridge was added to bridge the gap between the two sides.

This map is 100% symmetrical and features the Measure textures for a clean artistic style. dm_vertigo is a mid to close quarters map but also has some snipers nests. This map also has what is called *DMM or Digital Molecular Matter. It is not true DMM but has elements that true DMM hosts. DMM is the ability not to just break an object, but to individually break down pieces of the structure eventually into rubble. This makes game play varied fun.

*An example of DMM: There are barriers that completely hide the player when hiding behind it. But if you start shooting off pieces of the barrier you can start to see the player and eventually kill him.

The paper was about stoping gang violence so the guy suggested to make and arena and put the gangs into it and have them battle it out.  So i thought a paintball field would be perfect for it except the bunkers are made of metal.  So yeah, here it is, I hope you enjoy it!

This map is a small remake of my other map, dm_tunnels. This version of the map now has added routes and hallways to prevent bots and human players from crowding up one spot all the time. There are now multiple routes that can be taken instead of the regular head-on route.
